CBRE Western Australian Retail Investments as exclusive selling agents are pleased to present Ampol Kwinana Beach; a near new truckstop and service station perfectly positioned to service the Kwinana Port and Industrial hub.

Secured by a 15 year lease to Ampol Fuel, Ampol Truckstop & Service Station, Kwinana Beach offers a long term income stream with strong annual rental growth.

Located  within the suburb of Kwinana Beach, this property is set to benefit from the high level of activity and growth in the surrounding industrial area, which also includes Kwinana Bulk Jetty & Terminal just 2.5km* from the site. Kwinana Beach has a well established population which is forecast to increase by 3.35% by 2030.

Ampol Truckstop & Service Station, Kwinana Beach is offered For Sale via an Expressions of Interest.
